Gehenna. Requires at least 1 other Gehenna event in play.
Each imbued can have (and use) 1 power card for which he or she does not meet the requirements. An imbued who performs a successful action can gain one conviction [1 CONVICTION] from his or her ash heap. An imbued can gain only one conviction [1 CONVICTION] this way each turn.
{Added to the V:EKN banned list on the 1st of January, 2008.}

