Only usable if playing for ante.
Successful referendum means each Methuselah decides whether to ante the next card in his or her library or be ousted from the game. Decisions should be made simultaneously, as follows: each Methuselah holds out a hand with zero or one blood in it. Open hands simultaneously. A pool in a Methuselah's hand indicates that he or she chooses not to be ousted.
{Added to the V:EKN banned list on the 9th of January, 1995.}

Requires a prince or justicar.
Choose a new seating order. Successful referendum means each Methuselah takes his or her new seat.
